{"id": "1480844678327701534", "channel_id": "1480844678327701534", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：徐EP·不梦乡志异 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜OST：徐EP·不梦乡志异**\n让妾身想想， 今天的故事，要说什么呢……\n啊，妾身知道了，给小小姐和小先生们的故事应该是~\n夜半莫讲亏心错，三更冤魂上房梁。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n企划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"Xu EP: Strange Tales from the Dreamless Land\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: Xu EP: Strange Tales from the Dreamless Land**\nLet me think... what story shall I spin for you today?\nAh, I have it. A tale for the little lords and ladies...\n\"Recount no crime at midnight’s chime, lest the souls you wronged begin their climb.\"\n\nProject: B.I.A.V. Studio\nComposer: F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2026-03-10T08:28:04.077000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1480844678780682334", "filename": "OST-.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1858728}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480844884406440027", "channel_id": "1480844678327701534", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**1. 玄女无相-Shapeless Goddess-**\n\n古古怪，怪怪古，亡妻三更爬出土，浪子负心锅里煮。\n无相的神女愿救苦，割面剖怀取郎骨，献我堂前无上主。\n\nOld and strange, strange and old! The dead wife crawls from the midnight mold.\nThat faithless rake, so bold and cruel—We'll toss him in the pot to boil.\nOur Shapeless Goddess hears her cry, She'll flay his face, She'll drain the guy!\nWe'll carve his chest and take his bone, to lay before our Lady's throne.", "timestamp": "2026-03-10T08:28:53.210000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1480844883551060051", "filename": "0.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2044209}, {"id": "1480844883957780591", "filename": "01._-Shapeless_Goddess-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 16617490}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480845066133049397", "channel_id": "1480844678327701534", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**2. 珠露-Pearled Dew-**\n\n最多不过你切她，她杀你，共赴黄泉做对鸳鸯鬼。\n休休，不必愁。\n\nAt most, you slice and she slaughters; a pair of lovers bound for the Yellow Springs.\nPeace, peace—let your sorrows cease.", "timestamp": "2026-03-10T08:29:36.537000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1480845065172811888", "filename": "02._-Pearled_Dew-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 17007820}, {"id": "1480845065961345256", "filename": "1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2029876}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480845160777515018", "channel_id": "1480844678327701534", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**3. 狐鬼谈-Discourse of Fox and Specter-**\n\n若见狐鬼夜谈，宜覆面掩耳，敬而远之。\n\nShould you happen upon a Fox and a Specter in their midnight discourse: veil your face, cover your ears, and hold them at a reverent distance.", "timestamp": "2026-03-10T08:29:59.102000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1480845160064749619", "filename": "2.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2046013}, {"id": "1480845160412745728", "filename": "03._-Discourse_of_Fox_and_Specter-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 10470636}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480845304592072734", "channel_id": "1480844678327701534", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**4. 她▼的眼▼-Her ▼ ▼▼Eye ▼-**\n\n她祂她她她祂祂祂祂她她母亲母美丽的眼睛母亲母亲母亲亲亲亲亲母亲母亲母亲她祂祂她她她她▼▼▼\n\nShe. It. She. She. She. It. It. It. It. She. She. Mother. Muma. Beautiful eyes. Mother. Mother. Mother. Muma. Muma. Muma. Mother. Mo▼▼▼r. She. It. It. She. ▼▼e. Sh▼. S▼e. ▼▼▼", "timestamp": "2026-03-10T08:30:33.390000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1480845303769993266", "filename": "04._-Her_Eye_-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 34628676}, {"id": "1480845304273047664", "filename": "3.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2030194}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480845521089331303", "channel_id": "1480844678327701534", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**5. 还魂-The Soul’s Return-**\n\n吉时将至，开棺起椁——大变活人。\n\nThe auspicious hour draws nigh. Unseal the coffin, raise the shroud—and behold the great revival.", "timestamp": "2026-03-10T08:31:25.007000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1480845520011530240", "filename": "4.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2031705}, {"id": "1480845520707653683", "filename": "05._-The_Souls_Return-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 24460056}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480845535752491080", "channel_id": "1480844678327701534", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**6. 访罗山-To Mount Luo-**\n\n书接上回，那无头蝇似的郎君不知死，就只好任他……拜一拜酆都，访罗山。\n\nTo resume our tale: that gentleman, blundering like a headless fly, knew not his own end. There was naught to do but to let him… pay his respects at Fengdu, and find his rest upon Mount Luo, the Seat of the Dead.", "timestamp": "2026-03-10T08:31:28.503000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1480845534343204915", "filename": "06._-To_Mount_Luo-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 17244402}, {"id": "1480845535274336287", "filename": "5.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2032434}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480845647455453254", "channel_id": "1480844678327701534", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**7. 琉璃叹-Lament of the Glass-**\n\n大都好物不坚牢，凄凄苦苦，穷极无聊。\n\nThe finest things in this world are never robust. All is bitterness, all is grief... an eternity of profound tedium.", "timestamp": "2026-03-10T08:31:55.135000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1480845646666662009", "filename": "6.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2042160}, {"id": "1480845646973112381", "filename": "07._-Lament_of_the_Glass-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 21995082}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
